#

Classic Spaghetti Aglio e Olio

20 min
$5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy (if cheese added)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan (if no cheese added)

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseQuick Meal

Tags:

ItalianPastaQuick Meal

Description

A simple, yet flavorful pasta dish made with garlic, olive oil, and a touch of red pepper flakes.

Ingredients

  • spaghetti: 200g
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • olive oil: 1/2 cup
  • red pepper flakes: 1 tsp
  • parsley (fresh): 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • parmesan cheese (optional): to taste
